Parallels Desktop 10 for Mac lets you seamlessly run Windows and Mac applications side-by-side, without rebooting.

Enjoy the latest OS X features in Windows apps, like Dictation and gestures. Parallels Desktop 10 for Mac delivers an even more immersive environment for gaming, music, movies, with support for Retina display, Surround Sound 7.1 and superior 3D graphics rendering speeds.

In addition to Windows 8, other OSes can also be run in Parallels Desktop 10 for Mac, including Windows 7, Windows Vista, Windows XP, Windows 98, Linux, and Google Chrome OS.


Run Windows on Your Mac
Parallels Desktop 10 for Mac is the best solution for running Windows apps on a Mac

Parallels Desktop 10 for Mac is the world's easiest, fasted and most powerful solution for people who need regular access to many apps on both Windows and Mac from a single machine without rebooting. From PC-only games to productivity software, Parallels Desktop 10 for Mac has you covered.

If you love the look & feel of Mac OS, make Windows invisible while still using its applications. If you're new to Mac, keep the familiar Windows background and controls on your Mac. Either way, run Windows and Mac applications side-by-side with no compromises in performance.
